snippet.title: Waves 2: Notorious - Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Hack into Corporate Networks, upload viruses, steal their secrets and become Notorious in this Cyberpunk Bullet Hell Twin Stick Shooter.

http://wavesthegame.com/

Waves 2: Notorious takes place in a Cyberpunk version of the internet where everything is neon and incredibly deadly.

Alpha 7 Adds new enemies, gameplay mechanics, items and multiplayer to the game.

You can get the game in Early Access on Steam right now (Windows PC and Linux)
